00:00:09.602 --> 00:00:13.134
All right, so right when
you look at it you're like,

00:00:13.134 --> 00:00:15.267
"Oh wow, if this was just a sine of x,

00:00:15.267 --> 00:00:16.877
"not a sine squared of x.

00:00:16.877 --> 00:00:19.094
